1
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:14,340
=The Origin of Eternity=

2
00:00:14,780 --> 00:00:17,580
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:46,080 --> 00:00:47,440
Actually, repaying you with my body

4
00:00:48,320 --> 00:00:50,520
was just the excuse I used
for not being able to control myself.

5
00:00:52,240 --> 00:00:54,040
I told you to exchange
your body with the things you desire

6
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,480
out of spite too.

7
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:22,440
Bai Ze is a hostage from
the Ling Empire.

8
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,800
The prisoner army had experienced
the uprising of Lord Yong.

9
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,720
There are still 80,000
prisoners of war from the Ling Empire.

10
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,760
Your Majesty, if you grant Bai Ze
the tiger tally now,

11
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:31,200
you'll be releasing the captured tiger
back to its den.

12
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:34,080
Please think twice!

13
00:01:34,480 --> 00:01:36,720
Bai Ze will go to war against
the Ling Empire

14
00:01:36,760 --> 00:01:38,080
to avenge his parents.

15
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,200
His motive is understandable.

16
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,040
He requested the prisoner army from me
for two reasons.

17
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:45,480
First, those prisoners of war are
familiar with the Ling Empire's tactics.

18
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,160
Second, he's unwilling to sacrifice
the army of Great Sheng.

19
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,760
Do not make groundless conclusions.

20
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:58,080
Your Majesty, Bai Ze isn't one of us.

21
00:01:58,520 --> 00:01:59,920
I'm sure he has an ulterior motive.

22
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:02,480
Your Majesty, please think twice!

23
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,800
The uprising of Lord Yong
has already proven

24
00:02:06,240 --> 00:02:08,640
that Bai Ze is loyal to me.

25
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,760
Right now, the Ling Empire is in chaos.

26
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,120
Unexpected things might happen.

27
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:15,120
Your Majesty, even if you wish
to aid Bai Ze,

28
00:02:15,320 --> 00:02:18,800
why don't you do so after the
internal struggle is over?

29
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:20,240
Speed is the soldier's asset.

30
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,360
How could we only attack them after
Third Prince has stabilized his throne?

31
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:24,840
Anyway,

32
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,440
I've already made up my mind.

33
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:28,760
Save your breath.

34
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:32,120
Your Majesty, if you insist on doing so,

35
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,240
I...

36
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:36,400
I will take my own life!

37
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:40,440
Sir, please stop!

38
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,520
Enough!

39
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:45,080
Bai Ze, the hostage of Ling Empire,
seeks an audience!

40
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,160
Greetings, Your Majesty.

41
00:02:51,840 --> 00:02:52,400
You...

42
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,400
You devious scum

43
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,480
who tried to bewitch our empress here!

44
00:02:56,720 --> 00:02:57,600
How dare you taint the imperial court

45
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:59,000
with your presence!

46
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:06,240
The Third Prince of the Ling Empire
had usurped the throne

47
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,520
and murdered my mother.

48
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,520
He and I are sworn enemies now.

49
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:12,000
Your Majesty, if you grant me
the tiger tally,

50
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:14,000
after I've avenged my parents,

51
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,440
I will use my empire as our dowry

52
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,600
to marry you

53
00:03:17,600 --> 00:03:18,600
and stay by your side forever!

54
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,640
This!

55
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,640
If I go against my promise,

56
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,360
I shall suffer a terrible death!

57
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,440
There's no need for such a vicious vow.

58
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:41,080
Ever since what happened
within the Heavenly Dungeon,

59
00:03:41,280 --> 00:03:42,440
I'd decided

60
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,480
that I'd trust you forever.

61
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:46,640
Your Majesty.

62
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:48,200
Say no more.

63
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,200
Bai Ze,

64
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,320
I'll grant you the tiger tally
to the prisoner army.

65
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,880
May you return early

66
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,840
and marry me.

67
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:12,620
(Unification Hall)

68
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:21,720
War

69
00:04:21,840 --> 00:04:23,000
is dangerous.

70
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,640
Please mind your safety.

71
00:04:28,760 --> 00:04:29,560
All right.

72
00:04:31,640 --> 00:04:33,240
Remember to write to me

73
00:04:33,480 --> 00:04:35,000
so that I can know your progress.

74
00:04:36,360 --> 00:04:37,160
All right.

75
00:04:55,440 --> 00:04:56,240
Your Majesty.

76
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,240
Don't you have anything

77
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,320
to say to me?

78
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:13,720
This time, you do intend to marry me,

79
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:15,520
right?

80
00:05:22,800 --> 00:05:23,720
Prepare your wedding gown

81
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:25,400
and wait for my return.

82
