it's already past midnight.

85
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,440
It's time for you to sleep.

86
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:47,840
What do you think
Bai Ze is doing right now?

87
00:06:49,280 --> 00:06:51,480
